data.description: This is a beautiful private place. All fenced in and some cross fencing.  Has two primary suites, one upstairs and one downstairs. perfect for the in laws or family members. Hot tub in a private area behind the house. Chicken coops. garden area that is fenced.  Come enjoy the peaceful mornings or the pleasant evenings on the patios. Close to BLM and only about 6 miles from the reservoir.
